These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-1::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, sunflower, tulip, poppy, azalea
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, hot-chocolate, cola, lemonade, milk
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person who growstulip is not the person drinking tea##6
 3. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking cola is not the person who growsmarigold##6
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 9. the person drinking milk is not the person who growspoppy##6
10. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
11. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the person who growssunflower is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who growsamaryllis##2
13. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
14. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who growstulip##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |      5      |      6      |
| Hobby         | tulip | azalea | marigold     | sunflower | amaryllis | poppy |
| Nationality   | cola    | tea   | lemonade | milk | hot-chocolate    | iced-tea   |

