.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: trance, r&b, rock, gospel, electronic, folk
There are 6 different nationalities: american, british, dutch, indonesian, brazilian, turkish
 1. the turkish is in an odd position##4
 2. the turkish is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan gospel is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 4. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the fan trance##5
 5. the fan electronic is on the left of the fan gospel##1
 6. the fan r&b is on the left of the indonesian##1
 7. the fan folk is on the right of the fan r&b##1
 8. the british is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 9. the fan gospel is on the left of the fan r&b##1
10. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
11. the fan electronic is in an odd position##4
12. the indonesian is on the left or right of the british##3
13. the dutch is the fan gospel##1
14. the fan rock is not the dutch##6
15. the fan trance is between the american and the turkish##2
16. the turkish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |    3    |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Food    | rock | trance     | electronic   | gospel | r&b      | folk  |
| Hobby   | turkish   | brazilian | american | dutch  | british | indonesian |

