.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-3::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, apricot, ebony, turquise, pink
The people have 6 different jobs:  nurse, teacher, engineer, firefighter, coach, social-worker
 1. the person who likes pink is the engineer##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is not the social-worker##6
 3. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the firefighter##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is the coach##1
 6. the firefighter is between the social-worker and the person who likes turquise##2
 7. the engineer is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 8. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5
 9. the nurse is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes pink is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6    |
| Nationality   | turquise  | ebony | aquamarine    | apricot | blood-red | pink |
| Sport         | teacher | firefighter | social-worker | coach     | nurse  | engineer    |

