 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person who growsbellflower##6
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
11. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
13. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
14. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
