 7. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating grapefruit##2
 8. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 9. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
10. the person eating mango is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5

.:: Answer ::.
