 2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
 6. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
 7. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the horse is not the person eating cucumber##6
10. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the dog is the person eating cucumber##1
12. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
13. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |      3      |      4      |     5      |    6    |
