 3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
 4. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 7. the person playing monopoly is not the owner of the goat##6
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 9. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
12. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
13. the owner of the horse is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing go##2
14. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
15. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

