 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 5. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person playing bridge##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
10. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person playing chess##1
12. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
13. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
14. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |    3    |  4   |     5      |   6   |
