10. the person who likes amber is the person playing domino##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
12. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes apricot##1
13. the person playing billiard is not the person who likes light-blue##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |   4    |    5    |      6      |
| Beverage      | apricot | amber | white | ebony | light-blue | azure |
| Music-Genre   | scrabble  | domino   | backgammon | billiard  | canasta  | poker        |

