.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-19::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, orchid, balloon-flower, bellflower, marigold, amaryllis
The people have 6 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, writing, camping, drawing, reading
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 5. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
10. the person who growsorchid is the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
13. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
14. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
