.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-20::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: spy, horror, adventure, western, thriller, time-travel
6 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, fish, goat, mouse, horse
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
 4. the person watching thriller movies is not the owner of the mouse##6
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 6. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
 9. the owner of the horse is not the person watching horror movies##6
10. the owner of the fish is the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
12. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
13. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
14. the owner of the frog is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | thriller | time-travel | adventure | spy | horror | western |
| Music-Genre   | frog | fish        | mouse     | horse | goat      | guinea-pig |

 